Privacy Policy
Last updated: [DD Month YYYY]

1. Introduction
Welcome to DigiEd (“we”, “our”, “us”). We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use and safeguard the information you provide when using our website https://www.digied.in
.

2. Information we collect
When you register for a free counselling session or enroll in our courses, we may collect the following details:

Name

Email address

Mobile number

3. How we use your information
We use this information to:

Contact you to schedule free counselling sessions.

Share information about our digital marketing courses.

Send updates, reminders and learning-related communication.

We will not sell or rent your personal data to any third party.

4. Data storage
Your details are stored securely in our internal systems (e.g., Excel records maintained by our team). We take reasonable steps to prevent unauthorized access.

5. Sharing with third parties
We do not share your personal information with third parties, except where required by law.

6. Your rights
You can request us to update or delete your details anytime by contacting us.

7. Cookies & website data
Our website may use cookies or analytics tools to understand traffic and improve user experience. These do not collect personally identifiable details.

8. Updates to this policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The latest version will always be available on this page.

